{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11262", "repo": "rails", "body": "agree with @al2o3cr `serialize` is customizable, you can choose a lot of features which should be wrapped:\r\n\r\n```\r\nclas SomeModel < ActiveRecord::Base\r\n  class SymbolWrapper\r\n    def self.load(string)\r\n      string.to_sym\r\n    end\r\n\r\n    def self.dump(symbol)\r\n      symbol.to_s\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\n\r\n  serialize :value, SymbolWrapper\r\nend\r\n```", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d6ebbd3543c151008325"}, "issue_id": 11262, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/20495837", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11262#issuecomment-20495837", "updated_at": "2013-07-04T23:01:45Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg", "login": "pftg", "gravatar_id": "712a9cc852c438c0873ef0a98f749f2e", "html_url": "https://github.com/pftg", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/712a9cc852c438c0873ef0a98f749f2e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F58adcd3cfec4758f40b142a29c054d55.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 125715, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-07-04T23:01:45Z", "id": 20495837, "owner": "rails"}
